item.title: CVE-2020-2196|2024-08-04T07:01:41.041Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20selenium%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Selenium Plugin 3.141.59 and earlier has no CSRF protection for its HTTP endpoints, allowing attackers to perform all administrative actions provided by the plugin.
